=== group_formation.glp ===
Group formation protocol.
Goal: social_graph(Id, [msg(user, Id, create_group(Name, Friends))|In], Fs)

Founder-administered model: users create groups with selected friends.
Group identifier is (founder, name), preventing naming conflicts.

Phases:
1. Create group streams
2. Send invitations through friend channels
3. Members receive invitation with attestation
4. User accepts/rejects

Cases: social graph extension, attestation guards, group identity
